Package: libdaemon
Version: 0.14-5
Depends: libc
Source: feeds/packages/libs/libdaemon
SourceName: libdaemon
Section: libs
SourceDateEpoch: 1775319833
Maintainer: Ted Hess <thess@kitschensync.net>
